updating git repository
-----------------------
cd ~/run15
git pull

daily update
------------
cd ~/run15/voltage_stability
./update
type "./update help" for special arguments
 - use "month" and "day" to specify which day you want to look at
 - use "timestart" and "timestop" to specify a specific time range, 
   where the default values are "timestart=0" for the previous midnight
   and "timestop=0" for the present time
